headline: Synchrony Announces More Than $1.5 Million in Grants to Stamford Nonprofits, Joins Mayor Simmons to Celebrate Spring with Daffodil Blooms
summary: In a vibrant celebration of spring and community spirit, Synchrony (NYSE: SYF), a premier consumer financial services company headquartered in Stamford, together with Mayor Caroline Simmons, Stamford Downtown and Stamford Parks Community Partnership, today celebrated the blooming of hundreds of daffodils planted across Downtown Stamford through a contribution from Synchrony.
